@page "/"

<PageTitle>Medicine Manager</PageTitle>

<h1>Medicine Manager</h1>

<p>Welcome! This app lets you manage medicines and their intake schedules.</p>

<ul>
    <li><a href="/medicines">Medicines</a> — add and manage your medicines</li>
    <li><a href="/schedules">Intake Schedules</a> — define when and how often each medicine is taken</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<p class="text-muted fst-italic">
    This project is a starting point for the <strong>EF Core 101</strong> workshop.
    Data is currently stored in JSON files. Your task is to replace the
    <code>JsonFileRepository</code> with an Entity Framework Core implementation.
</p>

